@startuml
' Diagram: F08 - Duyet hoac tu choi thanh toan goi app (Sequence)
' Status: VERIFIED
' Baseline: HEAD 8ca9ec7
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/DuyetThanhToan/Index.cshtml.cs: OnGetAsync(), LoadStatsAsync(), LoadListAsync(), OnGetPendingSnapshotAsync(), OnPostApproveAsync(), OnPostRejectAsync()
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/DuyetThanhToan/Index.cshtml: polling PendingSnapshot
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Models/YeuCauThanhToan.cs
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Models/DangKyApp.cs
' Note: Sequence da doi ve dung owner method cua PageModel, bo nhan vat helper gia, va bo sung nhanh lyDo bat buoc khi reject.
' Note: Sequence khong liet ke cau SQL; chi the hien handler, helper method, va thao tac persistence chinh.
title F08 - Duyet hoac tu choi thanh toan goi app

actor Admin
boundary "DuyetThanhToan.cshtml JS" as JS
control "DuyetThanhToan IndexModel" as IndexModel
participant "AppDbContext\n<<persistence>>" as DbContext
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Admin -> IndexModel: OnGetAsync(tab, search, pkg, msg, err)
IndexModel -> IndexModel: LoadStatsAsync()
IndexModel -> DbContext: ToListAsync()
DbContext -> DB: read grouped request stats
DB --> DbContext: rows
DbContext --> IndexModel: grouped stats
IndexModel -> IndexModel: LoadListAsync()
IndexModel -> DbContext: ToListAsync()
DbContext -> DB: read request rows for current tab
DB --> DbContext: rows
DbContext --> IndexModel: DanhSach
IndexModel --> Admin: render stats + request table

loop JS polling snapshot
  JS -> IndexModel: OnGetPendingSnapshotAsync()
  IndexModel -> DbContext: CountAsync()
  DbContext -> DB: read pending snapshot
  DB --> DbContext: count
  DbContext --> IndexModel: count
  IndexModel -> DbContext: FirstOrDefaultAsync()
  DbContext -> DB: read latest pending row
  DB --> DbContext: latest row
  DbContext --> IndexModel: latest row
  IndexModel --> JS: JSON Count, LatestId, LatestTransferContent
end

alt admin duyet
  Admin -> IndexModel: OnPostApproveAsync(yeuCauId)
  IndexModel -> DbContext: FirstOrDefaultAsync()
  DbContext -> DB: read target request row
  DB --> DbContext: request row
  DbContext --> IndexModel: request row
  IndexModel -> DbContext: FirstOrDefaultAsync()
  DbContext -> DB: read active DangKyApp row
  DB --> DbContext: active subscription row
  DbContext --> IndexModel: active subscription row
  note right of IndexModel
    OnPostApproveAsync() computes
    mocBatDau and NgayHetHan.
  end note
  IndexModel -> DbContext: Add(DangKyApp)
  DbContext --> IndexModel: tracked entity
  IndexModel -> DbContext: SaveChangesAsync()
  DbContext -> DB: persist approval result
  DB --> DbContext: saved
  IndexModel --> Admin: Redirect ?tab=cho_duyet
else admin tu choi
  Admin -> IndexModel: OnPostRejectAsync(yeuCauId, lyDo)
  alt lyDo blank
    IndexModel --> Admin: Redirect ?tab=cho_duyet&err=...
  else lyDo valid
    IndexModel -> DbContext: FirstOrDefaultAsync()
    DbContext -> DB: read target request row
    DB --> DbContext: request row
    DbContext --> IndexModel: request row
    IndexModel -> DbContext: SaveChangesAsync()
    DbContext -> DB: persist reject result
    DB --> DbContext: saved
    IndexModel --> Admin: Redirect ?tab=tu_choi
  end
end
@enduml
